Bloomberg Digital Archive (BLM 001)

Digitize the complete archive of Mayor Bloomberg's time in office. This includes video tape, audio files, photographs and documents.

Overview

Assets

Details

You have made changes to project specifications. These changes will be applied to all future work orders created under this project.

 

Existing work orders will NOT be changed.

 

If you need to change the specifications for an existing work order, you must make those changes within the work order itself.
